# Marketing Component System

Canonical reference: `docs/component-system.md`

## Pages

- Export `metadata` from `page.tsx`.
- Compose with `PageShell` + `PageHero` + domain sections when using the standard marketing chrome.
- No raw `container` or section `py-*` on route files.
- No inline `italic text-brand-turquoise` accent spans — use `SectionHeader` / `PageHero` `accent` prop.

## Sections

- Use `MarketingSection` + `SectionHeader` + content.
- Import primitives from `@/components/marketing/primitives`.

## CTAs

- Signup/card flows: `GetCardCta` or `SlugClaimCta`.
- Other primary actions: `Button variant="brandPrimary"`.

## FAQs

- `FaqAccordion` + data from `src/content/`.

## Typography

- `import { type } from "@/lib/typography"` in TSX (synced with `@utility` in `globals.css`).

## Spacing contract

Tokens in `globals.css` (`--marketing-*`) → primitives → sections. No raw `container` / `py-*` / `pt-*` on route files.

| Variant | Utility |
|---------|---------|
| Gutter | `px-marketing-gutter-x md:px-marketing-gutter-x-md` via `MarketingContainer` |
| Section default / compact / hero | `py-marketing-section-y` / `py-marketing-section-y-compact` / `pt-marketing-page-top pb-marketing-hero-bottom` |
| Page shell | `pt-marketing-page-top pb-marketing-page-bottom` |
| Header gaps | `mb-marketing-header-gap` (PageHero), `mb-marketing-header-gap-md` (SectionHeader) |
| Card grids | `gap-marketing-grid-gap md:gap-marketing-grid-gap-md` via `FeatureGrid` / `MarketingStaggerGrid` |
| Stacks | `gap-marketing-stack-gap`, `space-y-marketing-stack-gap-sm` (FAQ, dense feature rows) |
